author: Kuro
description: Have you ever wondered, how many commands/cogs does your bot has? Well this cog can help with that!
end_user_data_statement: This cog does not store any end user data.
install_msg:
Thanks for installing `CogCount`! Get started with `[p]count`.
This cog has docs! Check it out at <https://kuro-cogs.readthedocs.io/en/latest/cogs/cogcount.html>.
name: CogCount
short: A cog that shows how many commands/cogs the bot has.
